{"tid":101014,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友有個青梅竹馬，我如何是好？","createTime":"2017-01-30T13:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:59:06.000Z","uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"591e8215ada66320f932cce322d501de8f565967","tid":101014,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"女友有個青梅竹馬<br />\n我係一齊之前已經知<br />\n個男嘅同我女朋友阿哥好熟<br />\n個男成日去佢地屋企玩<br />\n佢地屋企人都好鐘意佢<br />\n點知今日...<br />\n個男嘅又去佢地屋企玩<br />\n我女朋友就同我講<br />\n點知夜晚佢好興奮同我講全家去睇戲<br />\n咁我都好開心，佢地一家人感情咁去<br />\n我就問一句個男有去？<br />\n女友答係呀，一齊睇戲，一齊食飯<br />\n個刻我心好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解個男有去睇戲，佢唔講，仲話全家一齊去睇戲<br />\n各位巴絲打，我如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc09a8f374c520c9555439a292e09154a812b2b","tid":101014,"uid":63996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"人地入左family zone <br />\n巴打咪諗咁多"},{"pid":"4c13d582174a0c5d9f92fb6ae647382c252545ee","tid":101014,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e20086ecbff30dd2ccb3c4b63364c2858176a4b","tid":101014,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"有咩驚"},{"pid":"dd90911e3c743ca7d339d2e83f1cae6c3336483a","tid":101014,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地入左family zone <br />\n巴打咪諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27941aa952ea34408b370f37afe46fe4ba579248","tid":101014,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔問佢就唔同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084d29a9eb6ff0cdf3942bd91e